Governor Seyi Makinde introduces new modern transportation system to Oyo State. The motor bike operators are currently jubilating for the kind gesture. A PRESS RELEASE FROM THE PDP SECRETARIAT READS: CHAIRMAN, OYRTMA, MOGAJI AKIN FAGBEMI RECEIVED DELIVERY OF OVER 1000 SHELTER KITS FOR COMMERCIAL MOTORCYCLE OPERATORS IN IBADAN TODAY, IN CONNECTION TO THE “ONE PASSENGER PER OKADA” CAMPAIGN, SPONSORED BY MR SULAIMAN AGBOOLA SIDOL SOLUTIONS. SEE PHOTOS BELOW Source